            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Grace to you and peace from God our Father"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And from the Lord, the Lord Jesus Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I thank my God always, making mention of you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my prayers, hearing of your love"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And of the faith which you have toward the Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord Jesus and to all the saints,"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That the fellowship of your faith may become"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Operative in the full knowledge"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of every good thing which is in us for Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For I had much joy and encouragement over your love,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Because the inward parts of the saints"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Have been refreshed through you, brother."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wherefore, having much boldness in Christ"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To charge you what is fitting,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Because of love I rather entreat,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Being such a one as Paul, the aged,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And now also a prisoner of Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A prisoner of Christ Jesus."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I entreat you concerning my child"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Whom I’ve begotten in my bonds,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Onesimus, who formerly was useless to you,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But now is useful both to you and to me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Onesimus, whom I have sent back to you—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Him, that is, my heart, my very heart;"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Whom I resolved to keep with myself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That on your behalf he might minister,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Might minister to me in the bonds of the gospel,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But without your mind I did not want to do anything,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That your goodness should not be of necessity,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But your goodness be voluntary."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For perhaps therefore he was separated from you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For an hour that you might fully have him forever,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No longer as a slave, but above a slave,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A beloved brother, especially to me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And how much more to you, both in the flesh,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Both in the flesh and in the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If then you hold me as a partner,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Receive him as myself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And if he has wronged, has wronged you in anything,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or owes anything, charge that to my account;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you hold me a partner, receive him as myself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And if he has wronged you, charge that to my account."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I Paul have written with my own hand,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I will repay; I will repay;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not to say to you that you owe me even your own self,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your own self besides."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, brother, may I have profit from you in the Lord;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Refresh my inward parts in Christ."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "9"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Having confidence in your obedience,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I wrote to you, knowing that you’ll do beyond what I say,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And at the same time also prepare me a lodging;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For I hope that through your prayers I shall be,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through your prayers I shall be graciously,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I shall be graciously given to you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "10"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Epaphras, my fellow-prisoner"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In Christ Jesus, greets you;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As do Mark, and Aristarchus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Demas, and Luke, my fellow-workers."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The grace of the Lord, of the Lord Jesus Christ"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be with your spirit, with your spirit."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "11"
    }
  ],
